      "id": "PopularPost339190",
      "post_content": "Limited all-star. Slap auras on it and go to town.  \nOn the negative side, I'm personally in favor of Hexproof, but they didn't even bother to justify it on this creature. [Gladecover Scout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gladecover Scout) and [Invisible Stalker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Invisible Stalker) are sneaky, [Aven Fleetwing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aven Fleetwing) is fast, [Slippery Bogle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slippery Bogle) is slippery... This one hides under water?",
      "posted_by": "Trygon_Predator",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost339190\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Limited all-star. Slap auras on it and go to town.<br/>On the negative side, I'm personally in favor of Hexproof, but they didn't even bother to justify it on this creature. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gladecover Scout\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gladecover Scout\">Gladecover Scout</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Invisible Stalker\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Invisible Stalker\">Invisible Stalker</a> are sneaky, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Aven Fleetwing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aven Fleetwing\">Aven Fleetwing</a> is fast, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slippery Bogle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slippery Bogle\">Slippery Bogle</a> is slippery... This one hides under water?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '339190'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy81247\">Trygon_Predator</span>\r\n                                (9/17/2013 2:21:55 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: le